          <title>Valentin Vacherot stuns Novak Djokovic and could face cousin in Shanghai Masters final</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SHANGHAI (AP) — Valentin Vacherot earned the biggest win of his career by beating a hobbled Novak Djokovic 6-3, 6-4 on Saturday to reach the Shanghai Masters final — where he could face his cousin. The 204th-ranked Vacherot, of Monaco, was an alternate in qualifying but is having a career week.]]></description>
